                     <interp inst="t17740413-61-person545" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , the wife of the prosecutor, deposed to the table cloths.</p>
               <p>- Cummings. I am servant to Mr. Hop, pawnbroker; on the 29th of March, the prisoner pawned a piece of silk and five table spoons at our house; I lent four pound ten shillings on them. (They are produced and deposed to by the prosecutor).</p>
               <p>The prisoner said nothing in her defence.</p>
               <p>For the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17740413-61-person546">
